sequenceDiagram
    actor Guard as Security Guard
    participant UI as JavaFX Monitoring Screen
    participant Service as MonitoringService
    participant DAO as DeviceLogDAO / DeviceDAO
    participant DB as Relational Database
    participant Audit as AuditService

    Guard->>UI: Search active device
    UI->>Service: findActiveIngress(criteria)
    Service->>DAO: query active log
    DAO->>DB: SELECT open device_log
    DB-->>DAO: Active ingress data
    DAO-->>Service: Active log
    Service-->>UI: Display active device details
    Guard->>UI: Confirm visual verification and log egress
    UI->>Service: logEgress(logId, currentUser)
    Service->>Service: Validate device is Inside with open ingress
    Service->>DAO: Update egress time and set campus_status Outside
    DAO->>DB: UPDATE device_logs; UPDATE devices
    Service->>Audit: record egress event
    Service-->>UI: Success or validation error

